CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 29, 1962, pg. 20, reads: "Limbo, Everybody! - Young Daniel Wray ducks under the limbo stick at the annual Christmas party of the American Woodmen. Limbo and twisting highlighted the afternoon of Christmas activities."
TitMainTitle: Two boys holding limbo stick, with Daniel Wray bending backward underneath it, and Deborah Allen next in line, at Christmas party sponsored by American Woodmen
